description: Number of asymmetric types of Boolean functions of n variables under action of complementing group C(n,2).
links: Index entries for sequences related to Boolean functions
formula: 1/(2^n)*Sum((-1)^j*2^C(j, 2)*[ n, j ]*2^(2^(n-j)), j=0..n), where [ n, j ] is Gaussian 2-binomial coefficient.
author: _Vladeta Jovovic_
